Re: What does 〜て　おきます mean?
by NileCat » Wed 09.08.2010 1:38 am Unfortunately for us foreign learners, in any language, there is no "same one". Every single word/idiom/phrase has a nuance somewhat differs from the others.宿題をするつもりです。(you aim to do / you are willing to do)
